      "CIN": "L31200KL1996PLC010010",
      "story": "V-Guard was founded in 1977 by Mr. Kochouseph Chittilappilly with a loan of INR 1,00,000 from his father. Initially they manufactured only voltage stabilizers in Kerala. Over time they expanded into Digital UPS, Inverter & Batteries, Water Heaters, Pumps, Wires & Cables, Fans, Kitchen Appliances, Switches, Air Coolers, and Water Purifiers. In less than four decades, V-Guard built a strong reputation for reliability. In 2018 a world-class fans-only manufacturing facility was set up in Roorkee, Uttarakhand; commercial production began in 2020 and ISO certification was obtained in 2021. V-Guard now focuses on smart home solutions and technologically advanced products. They serve customers across India through a network of distributors, dealers, retailers, and service centers.",
